## Decisions Made
- Plan State section is always rendered (even when fields are null) so users see at a glance whether to plan, resume, or execute.
- Hash-match check uses the same _plan_hash.py module that state-commit and execute use (single source of truth for hash equality).
- Recent ping-pong activity = last 3 lines of the active cycle's jsonl, summarized inline.
- /agent-atelier:init slash references replaced with `bash ${CLAUDE_PLUGIN_ROOT}/scripts/init-helpers.sh` (or pointers to /plan and /execute which auto-init).

